{"word":"H268 - אָחֹור - ʼâchôwr - aw-khore' - After","slug":"H268","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">אָחֹור</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>ʼâchôwr"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>aw-khore'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>After"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05D0;&#x05D7;&#x05E8;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#x05D0;&#x05D7;&#x05D5;&#x05E8; - 'a&#x0302;cho&#x0302;r  'a&#x0302;cho&#x0302;r</b> - <i>aw-khore', aw-khore'</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/H299\">H299</a>; the <i>hinder</i> part; hence (adverbially) <i>behind</i>, <i>backward</i>; also (as facing north) the <i>West: - </i>after (-ward), back (part, -side, -ward), hereafter, (be-) hind (-er part), time to come, without."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H309\">H309</a>, <a href=\"#/H310\">H310</a>, <a href=\"#/H312\">H312</a>, <a href=\"#/H313\">H313</a>, <a href=\"#/H314\">H314</a>, <a href=\"#/H315\">H315</a>, <a href=\"#/H316\">H316</a>, <a href=\"#/H3186\">H3186</a>, <a href=\"#/H319\">H319</a>, <a href=\"#/H322\">H322</a>, <a href=\"#/H323\">H323</a>, <a href=\"#/H325\">H325</a>, <a href=\"#/H326\">H326</a>, <a href=\"#/H327\">H327</a>"}]}